smul_def:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem smul_def {R : Type _} [SMul R β] (r : R) (x : α) :
    @has_smul.smul _ _ (e.has_smul R) r x = e.symm («expr • » r (e x)) :=
  rfl
#align smul_def smul_def
ring_equiv_symm_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃ » -/
theorem ring_equiv_symm_apply (e : «expr ≃ » α β) [Add β] [Mul β] (b : β) :
    by
    letI := equiv.has_add e
    letI := equiv.has_mul e
    exact (RingEquiv e).symm b = e.symm b := by intros ; rfl
#align ring_equiv_symm_apply ring_equiv_symm_apply
ring_equiv_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃ » -/
@[simp]
theorem ring_equiv_apply (e : «expr ≃ » α β) [Add β] [Mul β] (a : α) : (ring_equiv e) a = e a :=
  rfl
#align ring_equiv_apply ring_equiv_apply
pow_def:
theorem pow_def {N : Type _} [Pow β N] (n : N) (x : α) : @has_pow.pow _ _ (e.has_pow N) x n = e.symm (e x ^ n) :=
  rfl
#align pow_def pow_def

local_ring:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →+* » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃+* » -/
@[reducible]
protected theorem local_ring {A B : Type _} [CommSemiring A] [local_ring A] [CommSemiring B] (e : «expr ≃+* » A B) :
    local_ring B :=
  haveI := e.symm.to_equiv.nontrivial
  local_ring.of_surjective (e : «expr →+* » A B) e.surjective
#align local_ring local_ring
